  "title": "Staff Nurse (Hospital/ Clinic) - Entry Level",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide quality nursing care and support to patients according to clinical protocols and standards</li>\n  <li>Assist in patient admissions, discharges, and daily care activities</li>\n  <li>Administer medications and treatments safely</li>\n  <li>Support doctors during clinical procedures and patient assessments</li>\n  <li>Monitor patient conditions and report any significant changes</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate nursing records and documentation</li>\n  <li>Ensure a safe and clean environment for patients and staff</li>\n  <li>Participate in ongoing training and quality improvement activities</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><br></h3>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Diploma in Nursing</strong></li>\n  <li>Registered with Singapore Nursing Board (SNB)</li>\n  <li>Willing to work on <strong>rotating shifts</strong> </li>\n  <li>Team player with good interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Responsible, caring, and committed to patient welfare</li>\n  <li>Entry-level candidates and fresh graduates are welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
